      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Bootstrap the LLM video\n\n1. Start from a blank user perspective.\n2. Open the bootstrap lesson and explain why the handshake exists.\n3. Copy the onboarding handshake and paste it into the LLM.\n4. Show what the LLM learns: transaction shape, node editing rules, declaration -> port -> portal flow, and current Twilite vocabulary.\n5. Create or edit one small graph with the LLM so the audience sees the contract in action.\n6. End by moving into primitives or the product graph.\n\nKeep the whole video focused on one repeatable success path.",
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "launch-content-declaration"
        }
      }
    },
